{
  "id": "63c308aceb6cbf001e56e3be",
  "title": "InstaChordでGarageBand (Mac) のギター音源を鳴らす方法",
  "created": 1673726125,
  "updated": 1673778610,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c308aceb6cbf001e56e3be",
      "text": "InstaChordでGarageBand (Mac) のギター音源を鳴らす方法",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673727329
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a10f",
      "text": "from [InstaChord+GarageBand]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c30b30e1daa50000f0a146",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726768,
      "updated": 1673726768
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a110",
      "text": "[InstaChord]で[GarageBand] (Mac) のギター音源を鳴らす方法が分かった[shoya140.icon]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673727339
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a111",
      "text": "\t課題",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a112",
      "text": " \tInstaChordのMIDI Outはチャンネルが15, 16に設定されている",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a113",
      "text": " \tこれらをGarageBandのギターと同じ帯域 (？) の1, 2に合わせる必要がある",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a114",
      "text": "\t解決策",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a115",
      "text": "\t\tMIDI Out Ch. が1, 2の新しい音色を作る",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a116",
      "text": "\t\t(既存の音色を編集すると副作用がありそうなので念のため新しく作った)",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673727159
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a117",
      "text": "\t手順",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a118",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/6f7c2fd83fbba0b6dcd16e3a36afa9cf][https://gyazo.com/b04eab8a0f16e188b72a1c870aedb645][https://gyazo.com/f64834d0e5bfa16d3a0650907c2e3337]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a119",
      "text": " \tMenu > Custom Instrument > ---- を選択 > OUTPUT > MIDI CH. (PAD/BTN) をそれぞれ1, 2にして保存",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673727205
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a11a",
      "text": " \tGarageBandに入力する時はこの新規音色を使う",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c308ace1daa50000f0a11b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673726125,
      "updated": 1673726125
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c5c7e1daa500005e234f",
      "text": "さらに[Backspace.fm年忘れウルトラ忘年会SUPERライブ2022]を観て分かったこと[shoya140.icon]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673774536,
      "updated": 1673776861
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c5dde1daa500005e2351",
      "text": "\tInstaChordのMIDI Out Ch. が一般的な1ではなく15に設定されているのは、1を他のMIDI (カラオケ, etc.) のために空けておきたかったから",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673774557,
      "updated": 1673774659
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c644e1daa500005e2352",
      "text": "\tということは、他のMIDI端末と一緒に使う予定がなければ、上記の解決策の中で新しい音色を作らず既存の音色のチャンネルを上書きしても良い",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673774660,
      "updated": 1673775043
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c68fe1daa500005e2353",
      "text": "\t\tおかしくなったらリセット",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673774735,
      "updated": 1673776521
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c5c9e1daa500005e2350",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673774538,
      "updated": 1673774538
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c6b0aff09e0000dcc732",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673774768,
      "updated": 1673774770
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c6b2aff09e0000dcc734",
      "text": " この解釈が正しくて「Dmだけ音が鳴る」も正しければ、Dmだけチャンネルを間違えて送信してることになるね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673774770,
      "updated": 1673774800
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cbdae1daa50000195528",
      "text": " \tDmも同様に15で送信しているけど、DmにはGarageBandが15で入力を受け付けるデータが含まれているみたい[shoya140.icon]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776091,
      "updated": 1673776478
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cc2fe1daa50000195529",
      "text": " \t\t[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TSjey879tG8]",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776176,
      "updated": 1673776184
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cc30e1daa5000019552a",
      "text": "\t\t\tMIDI Ch. を変更できるLogic Proで検証してみた (GarageBandと同じソフトウェア音源)",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776177,
      "updated": 1673776222
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cc61e1daa5000019552b",
      "text": "\t\t\tMIDI Ch. を変えると音色が変わる",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776225,
      "updated": 1673776239
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cc6fe1daa5000019552c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t15にはD1より上の音が設定されていない",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776239,
      "updated": 1673776986
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cca4e1daa5000019552d",
      "text": "\t\t\tC0-D1にMIDI1ノートで和音が鳴る機能が登録されている",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776292,
      "updated": 1673776780
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3ccd8e1daa5000019552e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれは1-16で共通",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776344,
      "updated": 1673776538
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3ccfae1daa5000019552f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tDmの構成音にC0-D1が入っていた",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776379,
      "updated": 1673776783
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3cd24e1daa50000195530",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t従ってDm (あるいはInstaChordのPosを極端に下げた時) だけ音が鳴った",
      "userId": "585ba87ba2536e0011e1daa5",
      "created": 1673776420,
      "updated": 1673776465
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3c6b2aff09e0000dcc733",
      "text": "　　謎は解けた！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673774770,
      "updated": 1673778603
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3d5aaaff09e0000dcc754",
      "text": "　　 すごいトリッキーな謎だったなぁw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673778603,
      "updated": 1673778610
    },
    {
      "id": "63c3d5a2aff09e0000dcc753",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673778594,
      "updated": 1673778594
    }
  ]
}